data.description: Nestled in the serene Waldron Farms subdivision, this 4BR, 3BA haven offers modern comfort, spacious living, and a strong sense of community. With an updated kitchen, 3 BR down, a quiet backyard setting and a short drive to Murfreesboro amenities, you won't want to miss out on this incredible opportunity. Make sure to check out the private wooded area in the back yard. Enter into the woods to plan where the next tree fort or private fire pit will go.
